GemP18.name: GemP18
GemP18.desc: Turns your 1st Liquid Cauldron into a Dragonic Cauldron, or 2nd Liquid Cauldron if you bought this before. Dragonic Cauldrons give 2x Liquid Capacity, a bonus which stacks with the 1.5x from Bleach Liquid Cauldrons.

Pearl6.name: Pearl6
Pearl6.desc: You found a pair of what now? Where'd you find those, I don't remember stocking them... well, does it have a price tag? No? Eh lets just call it 1 gem... but the 2nd one is gonna cost ya extra!

GemP26.name: GemP26
GemP26.desc: Upgrades a random artifact you own to its ANCIENT form! 100% Success chance, no foolin! This item restocks every week. See Guild GP claim for when that happens.

GemP19.name: GemP19
GemP19.desc: Gives you one of the Following Obols: Amarok Obol (+4% DEF), Efaunt Obol (+5% Boss Damage), Slush Obol (+3% Skill Efficiency), Chizoar Obol (+4% Total Damage), or Troll Obol (+3% ALL STAT)

EquipmentRings32.name: EquipmentRings32
EquipmentRings32.desc: All kills in World 4 count for 1.30x for opening portals to the next map. Helps you get to World 5 faster! 30% Faster to be exact!
